"I also recommend the Bitcoin Developer Reference (<<web-dev-ref>>), for more"
" comprehensive documentation of Bitcoin."
msgstr ""
"Ich empfehle ausserdem die Bitcoin Developer Reference (<<web-dev-ref>>) als"
" umfassendere Dokumentation von Bitcoin."

#. type: Plain text
#: front-matter.adoc:370
