#. type: Plain text
#: ch10-segregated-witness.adoc:1286
msgid ""
"Why do lightweight wallets need the signatures of a legacy transaction to "
"verify that it’s included in a block?"
msgstr ""
"Warum brauchen Lightweight Wallets die Signaturen einer herkömmlichen "
"Transaktion, um zu verifizieren, dass sie Teil eines Blocks ist?"

